{"tid":1125724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"友愛邨六旬翁床單自縊亡 女友揭發報警","createTime":"2019-04-26T01:45:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T15:17:24.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4444f67af40c56c745c0d5fefa45e2b8785932a9","tid":1125724,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T01:45:06.000Z","msg":"屯門友愛邨一名六旬翁以床單上吊死亡，警方正調查其尋死原因。<br />\n<br />\n事發在昨晚8時許，一名65歲姓余的男子在愛樂樓一單位以床單上吊，其女友發現將他解下並報警，救護員到場證實事主已經不治。警方初步調查相信事件無可疑，現場未有檢獲遺書，正調查事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/987451-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E5%8F%8B%E6%84%9B%E9%82%A8%E5%85%AD%E6%97%AC%E7%BF%81%E5%BA%8A%E5%96%AE%E8%87%AA%E7%B8%8A%E4%BA%A1+%E5%A5%B3%E5%8F%8B%E6%8F%AD%E7%99%BC%E5%A0%B1%E8%AD%A6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F987451-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E5%258F%258B%25E6%2584%259B%25E9%2582%25A8%25E5%2585%25AD%25E6%2597%25AC%25E7%25BF%2581%25E5%25BA%258A%25E5%2596%25AE%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%25B8%258A%25E4%25BA%25A1%2B%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%258F%258B%25E6%258F%25AD%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E8%25AD%25A6&d=fAF%2FER2cs4qp%2F6NYk0BreFQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=e1d55b5c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F987451-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E5%258F%258B%25E6%2584%259B%25E9%2582%25A8%25E5%2585%25AD%25E6%2597%25AC%25E7%25BF%2581%25E5%25BA%258A%25E5%2596%25AE%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%25B8%258A%25E4%25BA%25A1%2B%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%258F%258B%25E6%258F%25AD%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E8%25AD%25A6&h=439a12b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/987451-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E5%8F%8B%E6%84%9B%E9%82%A8%E5%85%AD%E6%97%AC%E7%BF%81%E5%BA%8A%E5%96%AE%E8%87%AA%E7%B8%8A%E4%BA%A1+%E5%A5%B3%E5%8F%8B%E6%8F%AD%E7%99%BC%E5%A0%B1%E8%AD%A6</a>"},{"pid":"1861530151182c5b36140b0485c6ae9e9221d308","tid":1125724,"uid":5178,"like"